For converting pound to gram (imperial system).1lbsCO2/kWh=0.454gCO2/KWh\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$1{\mathrm{lbsCO}}_{2}/\mathrm{kWh}=0.454{\mathrm{gCO}}_{2}/\mathrm{KWh}$$\end{document}

For converting gram to kilogram (metric system).1gCO2/kWh=0.001kgCO2/kWh\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
